reg_info.full_title: R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 913: PERSONAL PROPERTY SECURITY ASSURANCE FUND

content.content: 1. One per cent of the fees received under the Act in respect of statements accepted for registration shall be paid into The Personal Property Security Assurance Fund.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 913, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. One per cent of the fees received under the Act in respect of statements accepted for registration shall be paid into The Personal Property Security Assurance Fund.  R.R.O. 1990, Reg. 913, s. 1.
